<HEAD>Marketing Students to Devise Census Strategy</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Marketing students in the nation's colleges
and universities will focus their skills on devising ways to
promote the 1990 Census.
   The Census was selected as the topic for the 1988-89 marketing
